Date: 2026-06-30

Request: CROSS-REQ-03 - Readiness & Ownership Alignment

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This file is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Purpose

This alignment model connects opportunity ownership, dependency ownership, nucleus readiness and escalation responsibility across Axodus.

It creates portfolio visibility only. It does not implement integrations, APIs, product functionality, MCP services, providers, governance execution, treasury execution, trading execution, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, wallet signing, on-chain writes or production readiness.

